* JDBC / ODBC\nConnections
** Supported Databases
***_ SQL Server, Oracle
***_ PostgreSQL, MySQL
***_ Any JDBC/ODBC driver
** Implementation
***_ Full or incremental loads
***_ Watermark columns for tracking
***_ Store credentials in Databricks secrets
** On-Premises Access
***_ ExpressRoute / VPN
***_ ADF with Self-Hosted IR
** When Still Relevant
***_ DB not in Lakeflow Connect
***_ Custom extraction logic needed
***_ Existing pipelines
@endmindmap
